enum groxide_test_api::Shape

pub enum Shape

An enum with data-carrying variants.

variants:
  Circle(f64)                                                 A circle with a radius.
  Point                                                       A point with no data.
  Rectangle { width: f64, height: f64 }                       A rectangle with width and height.

